INTRO                                             You see a friendly girl wearing a gold necklace with a single ruby. "Greetings, traveler! Welcome to the Bridgeway Inn and Pub! May I help thee, today?"                                                NAME                                              "Katy! 'Tis such a pleasure when someone comes to CHAT."                                                                                                                                                JOB                                               "I run the inn and pub. My job is to serve FOOD to the customers, as well as    provide a place to SLEEP. Of course, I like to CHAT, too!"                                                              BYE                                               "My pleasure! Please patronize us again sometime! Fare thee well!"                                                                                                                                                                                        "Sorry, I know little about that."                                                                                                                                                                      NO                                                "Ah, perhaps thee wish to CHAT! I love to talk with visitors!"                                                                                                                                          YES                                               "Dost thous need FOOD, SLEEP, or just wish to CHAT?"                                                                                                                                                    SLEEP                                             "A bargain at only 5gp a night! Sweet dreams." She shows you to your room.                                                                                                                              FOOD                                              "We hath BANBAN fruit, GRAPES, MUTTON, FISH, BREAD, FOWL, OATMEAL, APPLES,      CHEESE and RICE. Which wouldst thou like today?"                                                                        BANBAN                                            "'Tis most fresh!"                                                                                                                                                                                      GRAPES                                            "Plump and juicy!"                                                                                                                                                                                      MUTTON                                            "Carved only this morning!"                                                                                                                                                                             FISH                                              "A fresh catch!"                                                                                                                                                                                        BREAD                                             "I bake it myself, I do!"                                                                                                                                                                               FOWL                                              "Excellent duck, caught only a few hours ago. Very fresh."                                                                                                                                              OATMEAL                                           "A good choice. It art very nutritious."                                                                                                                                                                APPLES                                            "Big, ripe and red! We import them from topside, you know!"                                                                                                                                             CHEESE                                            "Cheddar is what we make here. It's delicious!"                                                                                                                                                         RICE                                              "Pre-cooked and ready to eat, a very nutritious snack."                                                                                                                                                 FAKEOUT                                           FAKEOUT?                                                                                                                                                                                                CHAT                                              Katy leans on the counter. "Did you know I've been COOKING here for so long     I've got a reputation that spans generations. It's true!"                                                               COOKING                                           "Well, it's a family tradition. We hath several members on our family who run   pubs and inns throughout the underland. My SISTERS, for example."                                                       SISTERS                                           She gives you a warm smile, happy that someone's interested in her job. "Well,  there's ELSI of the SUNRAY pub, and MOLLY of the GREEN GROX Inn."                                                       ELSI                                              "Elsi's a fine sister and a fine cook. She's up on level two, at the SUNRAY pub.Thou shouldst visit her sometime. Tell her I said hi!"                                                                  SUNRAY                                            "It's a nice establishment where thou canst find similar services like here."                                                                                                                           MOLLY                                             "She's the oldest of us sisters. They say we all look alike, but I think she hasnicer hair than I. Oh, well! Thou canst find her at the GREEN GROX Inn."                                                GREEN GROX                                        "It's another pub and inn, on the eastern part of this level. We calleth it     GROUND level, you know."                                                                                                GROUND                                            "That's 'cause we're at the bottom floor of the mountain." She peeks outside.   "Ah, 'tis wonderful we can see the sun here, streaming in from above!"                                                  